Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/moshpitsurfer/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc (OPTIONAL)

Copy pathogen plugin:
    
    cp ~/.vim/bundle/pathogen/autoload/pathogen.vim ~/.vim/autoload/.


Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update
